These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-7-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, sprite
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, august, april
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, photography
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, ebony, aquamarine
3 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, billiard
House: cottage, cape-cod, ranch-style
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, swisher, aristoff
 1. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the cain-smoker and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
 8. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the cottage house##1
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
11. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite    | mirinda   |
| Birthday          | april       | september | august      |
| Hobby         | photography | chess     | camping   |
| Color   | ebony        | aquamarine      | azure     |
| Game   | billiard  | monopoly    | bridge     |
| House           | cottage  | cape-cod  | ranch-style   |
| Cigar         | aristoff     | swisher  | cain |

