.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-7-2::.
3 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, backgammon
House: wooden, cottage, townhouse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bluemaster, dunhill
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy, scientific
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, amber, turquise
3 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, pony
City: boston, venice, rome
 1. the dunhill-smoker is the person who likes turquise##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching drama movies and the cottage house##2
 5. the wooden house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 6. the person who likes purple is not the owner of the ferret##6
 7. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
 9. the person who likes amber is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person playing mah-jongg##7
10. the person traveling to rome is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
11. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the owner of the cat##7
12. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
13. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |     3     |
| Game      | backgammon           | bridge        | mah-jongg    |
| House          | cottage        | townhouse     | wooden |
| Cigar           | dunhill | bluemaster | ritmeester |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific    | fantasy        | drama     |
| Color   | turquise        | amber           | purple      |
| Pet           | cat           | ferret         | pony      |
| City         | rome | boston     | venice   |

