.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, tea
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, go
House: modern, futuristic, colonial
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, yellow, brown
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, zinnia
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, sailing, lacrosse
 1. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person playing go##7
 2. the person who likes brown is not the person who growsaconite##6
 3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not the person who likes yellow##6
 6. the person drinking coffee is the colonial house##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
11. the modern house is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
12. the person playing backgammon is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | coffee          | tea         | soy-milk     |
| Game          | go          | backgammon      | scrabble       |
| House           | colonial | modern  | futuristic |
