House: cottage, townhouse, palace
 1. the cottage house is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
 3. the person traveling to colone is the person eating papaya##1
 4. the palace house is not the person watching zombie movies##6
 5. the lawyer is not the fan of salsa##6
 6. the person playing canasta is not the person traveling to colone##6
 7. the electrician is not the fan of reggae##6
 8. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 9. the person eating orange is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
10. the cottage house is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the cottage house and the lawyer##7
12. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
13. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
14. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
